Author: throwawhale-__-
Text: Yah. I don’t want anyone to worry or treat me differently, or think that I’m doing for attention or to get pity. It’s so socially isolating.

Author: LifeAsMagic
Text: !!!Me TOO!!! Same #s, age, years, same everything. It sucks... it's isolating and like a prison. And it's like you cant talk to anyone about it because you dont want to worry them and it feels almost shameful... I feel disgusted too. Tomorrow is a new day.
